**403** | Kh√іng c√≥ quyбїБn |\\n| `GET /exams` | вЭМ **403** | Kh√іng c√≥ quyбїБn |\\n| `GET /stadiums` | вЭМ **403** | Kh√іng c√≥ quyбїБn |\\n| `GET /payments` | вЭМ **403** | Kh√іng c√≥ quyбїБn |\\n| `GET /notify-configs` | вЭМ **403** | Kh√іng c√≥ quyбїБn |\\n| `GET /notify-contents` | вЭМ **403** | Kh√іng c√≥ quyбїБn |\\n| `GET /guests` | вЬЕ 200 | Public вАФ kh√іng cбЇІn auth |\\n\\n### рЯФі Root Cause вАФ Permission/Role Configuration\\n`admin2` ƒС∆∞бї£c seed nh∆∞ng **kh√іng c√≥ role/permission g√°n ƒС√Їng** trong database. C√°c endpoint nghiбїЗp vбї• (users, lessons, exams, payments...) ƒСбїБu check permission middleware v√† trбЇ£ 403.\\n\\n### вЬЕ ƒР√£ x√°c ƒСбїЛnh path fix:\\n```\\n1. G√°n role_id cho admin2 trong MongoDB\\n2. HoбЇЈc tбЇ°o seed role mбЇЈc ƒСбїЛnh cho admin2\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Pipeline:** HEALTHY вЬЕ\\n**Blocker:** CбЇІn fix permission seed cho admin2 вАФ cбЇІn lead quyбЇњt ƒСбїЛnh approach (seed script hay manual DB update).\\n\\nLead muбїСn fix permission bбЇ±ng c√°ch n√†o?\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 269,\n            \"output\": 886,\n            \"totalTokens\": 54007,\n            \"cacheRead\": 51905,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 947,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776149714071,\n          \"responseId\": \"062d17d30ee320bb036e66e89f6f4c0c\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"be602c5c\",\n            \"seq\": 21\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"label\": \"DTLX Full API T